{"id":308838,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/维权网-上海市民沈勇家连续遭到官商勾结的打砸/","date":"2013-08-14T11:03:57Z","modified":"2013-08-14T11:03:57Z","title":"维权网 | 上海市民沈勇家连续遭到官商勾结的打砸抢（图）　","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙小芸报道）<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>日、<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>日、<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>日</span><span>晚</span><span>上，上海上</span><span>访维权</span><span>人士沈勇位于浦</span><span>东</span><span>新</span><span>区</span><span>北蔡</span><span>镇</span><span>北艾路</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1765</span><span>弄<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span></span><span>号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">102</span><span>室的家中</span><span>连续</span><span>遭到</span><span>官商勾</span><span>结</span><span>的打</span><span>砸抢</span><span>行</span><span>动</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日</span><span>晚</span><span>上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>时许</span><span>，一群</span><span>歹</span><span>徒受北蔡</span><span>镇</span><span>政府指示冲到北蔡</span><span>镇</span><span>北艾路</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1765</span><span>弄<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span></span><span>号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">102</span><span>室</span><span>门</span><span>口用</span><span>铁</span><span>榔</span><span>头</span><span>把</span><span>一扇</span><span>铁门</span><span>和一扇防</span><span>盗门</span><span>一起</span><span>打落在地（有照片为</span><span>证</span><span>），</span><span>闯</span><span>入沈勇家中</span><span>敲碎抽水</span><span>马</span><span>桶</span><span>，水和</span><span>电</span><span>遭到</span><span>恶</span><span>意破坏</span><span>后无法使用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span>晚</span><span>上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>时</span><span>～</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分，一群</span><span>歹</span><span>徒又奉命</span><span>来</span><span>到沈勇家中把</span><span>玻璃</span><span>门</span><span>窗敲碎</span><span>，玻璃洒落一地，</span><span>电风</span><span>扇</span><span>敲坏后推倒在地，沈勇<span lang=\"EN-US\">80</span></span><span>岁</span><span>高</span><span>龄</span><span>的</span><span>母</span><span>亲</span><span>沈阿</span><span>宝</span><span>被</span><span>歹</span><span>徒打</span><span>伤</span><span>，</span><span>仰面朝天倒在玻璃碎片上，</span><span>桌</span><span>子被打破一</span><span>个</span><span>洞</span><span>，藏在碗</span><span>厨</span><span>里的一枚戒指和一</span><span>条项链</span><span>被</span><span>抢</span><span>走。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日</span><span>晚</span><span>上，</span><span>歹</span><span>徒第三次</span><span>闯</span><span>入沈勇家</span><span>扫荡</span><span>，</span><span>沈勇一家老小生命得不到保障，</span><span>因此，沈勇痛苦万分，不得不求</span><span>问</span><span>：“在</span><span>这个</span><span>法治</span><span>国</span><span>家里，官</span><span>员怎么</span><span>不</span><span>讲</span><span>法？在</span><span>这个</span><span>和</span><span>谐</span><span>社</span><span>会</span><span>里，</span><span>做出不和</span><span>谐</span><span>的事，</span><span>这</span><span>是什</span><span>么</span><span>世道？</span><span>说</span><span>的</span><span>与</span><span>做的完全</span><span>两</span><span>重天。”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>沈勇家遭受如此暴力</span><span>袭击并</span><span>非偶然，早在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>日，</span><span>拥</span><span>有</span><span>农</span><span>村宅基地上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">621</span><span>平方米房屋遭到上海市浦</span><span>东</span><span>新</span><span>区</span><span>政府强拆。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>年多</span><span>来</span><span>，沈勇全家老小无家可</span><span>归</span><span>，流浪街</span><span>头</span><span>。直至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span>日，沈勇住</span><span>进</span><span>自家的自留地上的房屋，却接二</span><span>连</span><span>三遭到北蔡</span><span>镇</span><span>政府派</span><span>歹</span><span>徒打</span><span>砸抢进</span><span>行迫害。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>沈勇站在被敲碎的玻璃</span><span>门</span><span>旁</span><span>边</span><span>呼求：“</span><span>请</span><span>求全人</span><span>类爱</span><span>好和平的人</span><span>们</span><span>，求求</span><span>你们</span><span>救救我</span><span>们</span><span>一家老小</span><span>吧</span><span>，我</span><span>们随时会</span><span>被</span><span>夺</span><span>去生命</span><span>，求求</span><span>你们</span><span>了，</span><span>谢谢</span><span>！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>求救人：沈勇</span><span>电话</span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13917961059</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-v5N-xbrv10Q/UgsRW5H8iWI/AAAAAAAAmys/ty7cCjNDRVY/s1600/176.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-v5N-xbrv10Q/UgsRW5H8iWI/AAAAAAAAmys/ty7cCjNDRVY/s320/176.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-dKO1ek9ickw/UgsRUpp6nvI/AAAAAAAAmyc/Y_4f_Jy9v-Y/s1600/%E6%8E%A5%E6%8A%A5%E5%9B%9E%E6%89%A7%E5%8D%951.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-dKO1ek9ickw/UgsRUpp6nvI/AAAAAAAAmyc/Y_4f_Jy9v-Y/s320/%E6%8E%A5%E6%8A%A5%E5%9B%9E%E6%89%A7%E5%8D%951.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-M9qFnveBJb4/UgsRU6pFpoI/AAAAAAAAmyg/BxyY8QMXVaE/s1600/%E6%8E%A5%E6%8A%A5%E5%9B%9E%E6%89%A7%E5%8D%952.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-M9qFnveBJb4/UgsRU6pFpoI/AAAAAAAAmyg/BxyY8QMXVaE/s320/%E6%8E%A5%E6%8A%A5%E5%9B%9E%E6%89%A7%E5%8D%952.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-MSoU0Jl--48/UgsRY2CQJfI/AAAAAAAAmy0/QwVM1lMbHKs/s1600/%E6%B2%88%E5%8B%87%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84